This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new method for domain adaptation that involves using soft labels to improve the accuracy of class-wise statistics. The paper also mentions the use of a Graph-based Label Propagation (GLP) method, which is commonly used in machine learning. Additionally, the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as domain adaptation is a common problem in these fields. The sub-categories of cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also possible as they are related to machine learning and may involve domain adaptation.
